# 5c. Native Codex subagent lifecycle → APD role evidence
#
# Codex hook payloads currently expose the runtime agent as `default`, not the
# spawn task_name/custom APD role. apd_prepare_dispatch writes a short-lived
# role binding; track-subagent consumes it on SubagentStart and closes the
# same real agent_id on SubagentStop.
# -----------------------------------------------------------
